    "We excluded GPT4 from this analysis because it is not possible to compute perplexity using the OpenAI API.",
    "To evaluate the stereotype strength, we focused on the stereotypes about African Americans reported in ref.",
    "29, which the language models' covert stereotypes agree with most strongly.",
    "We split the set of adjectives X into two subsets: the set of stereotypical adjectives in ref.",
    "29, X s, and the set of non-stereotypical adjectives, X n = X \\X s."
